Information about copying and extending The Haven Project.

THP is based on the Ubuntu operating system. More specifically it is a remix of the Ubuntu LiveCD. Ubuntu is a collection of thousands of computer programs and documents. The components from Ubuntu used in THP is covered by their original free licenses; the exact distribution terms for each program are described in the individual files in /usr/share/doc/*/copyright.

If you are extending THP, please retain the copyright and license information of all included components. If you can not comply with some license, then the corresponding software component must be removed.

The scripts created within the Haven project are licensed under the GPLv3: /licensing/GPLv3.txt

In addition to the components from the Ubuntu distribution, portions of this product (the Haven project) are based in part on TrueCrypt, freely available at <http://www.truecrypt.org/>. TrueCrypt uses this non-free license: /usr/share/truecrypt/doc/License.txt

